      <Text layoutX="57.0" layoutY="114.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Welcome the the game named &quot;WORLD OF INEQUALITY&quot;.&#10;&#10;You will start by picking a country to play in. &#10;You will then randomly start as a male or female, and have a random amount of start money, in that country.&#10;&#10;This game has two stages, a &quot;child&quot; stage and an &quot;adult&quot; stage.&#10;In the child stage you can read books, which can be bought in the shop, and you can work. &#10;The books will give you something called &quot;knowledge points&quot;. &#10;Knowledge points is something that decides how educated you are in the game. &#10;The more books you read, the smarter you will be. This will increase your salary when you work.&#10;To read a book you need to be in the &quot;school&quot; and then press on the book.&#10;&#10;In the adult stage you can ONLY work. Therefore it is important to make the right decisions in the child stage.&#10;&#10;Important information etc. will appear under &quot;Event&quot; in the overlay, watch it carefully!&#10;Watch out for sickness and injuries. Both will effect your salary when you work.&#10;When you get sick, you have a limited amout of turns to get healed at the hospital.&#10;To unlock the hospital press the &quot;appointment&quot; text in your inventory, when you are &quot;outside&quot;.&#10;&#10;When you sleep in your home you change stage. So when you sleep as a child, you will be an adult. &#10;When you sleep as an adult then you will die and the game is over.&#10;&#10;You can click on doors, signs, etc. Everything that stands a &quot;bit&quot; out." textAlignment="CENTER" wrappingWidth="1165.13671875">
